  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The capacity of concept formation is not well understood, even if a link is supposed with the
      functioning of the frontal lobes.

      Our aim is to better understand the cognitive mechanisms underlying this function and to try
      to correlate the performance with atrophy of the frontal lobe in neurodegenerative diseases
      involving this region (frontotemporal lobar degeneration and progressive supranuclear palsy).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
